{"tid":2290655,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我提倡新既民主制度","createTime":"2020-11-18T07:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T12:03:16.000Z","uid":59570,"like":7,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"3dec4db3903801bb2d6d2e4e68d01e6de965d23e","tid":2290655,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"今次既美國大選令我認為民主制度已經走到盡頭<br />\n<br />\n互聯網絡洗腦式光環宣傳凌駕咗大部分人思考能力<br />\n<br />\n冇獨立思考既一人一票已經玩爛咗<br />\n<br />\n因此，我提出新形式民主社會制度<br />\n<br />\n就係，所有擁有投票權既公民必須修讀過哲學<br />\n<br />\n以哲學邏輯打破洗腦手法<br />\n<br />\n如果要實踐呢個哲學形民主社會<br />\n<br />\n首先哲學要成為必修或選修課程<br />\n<br />\n可以讓市民係中學選修以進入有投票權既人生<br />\n<br />\n或者唔讀放棄投票權，當然日後可以選修返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎開放討論"},{"pid":"0d6572ffb8de679674ab87ab068adda02227a83e","tid":2290655,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fa34168ca8babf2cd2fa028a6e418155225ea3","tid":2290655,"uid":186177,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"到時變當年紅軍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cddaea0924f0f47f803aa523aac4564b5e5b99","tid":2290655,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"67fa34168ca8babf2cd2fa028a6e418155225ea3","tid":2290655,"uid":186177,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"到時變當年紅軍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"即係點？"},{"pid":"4697a8d52f895ecad200e41be9c9ade70376c29c","tid":2290655,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67fa34168ca8babf2cd2fa028a6e418155225ea3","tid":2290655,"uid":186177,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"到時變當年紅軍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif